### Register a new member
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "username": "john",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Register - missing email (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "",
  "username": "john",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Register - invalid email format (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "username": "john",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Register - duplicate email (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "username": "john2",
  "password": "secret123"
}
